ActProhibition on the Purchase of Residential Property by Non-Canadians Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Minister of Infrastructure and Communities as the Minister for the Purposes of the Prohibition on the Purchase of Residential Property by Non-Canadians Act
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2022-1104 of October 19, 2022; and (2) designating the Minister of INFRASTRUCTURE AND COMMUNITIES, a member of the King’s Privy Council for Canada, as the Minister for the purposes of the PROHIBITION ON THE PURCHASE OF RESIDENTIAL PROPERTY BY NON-CANADIANS ACT.
